                                    <p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: normal; margin: 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">
                                        <a href="{{ link_url }}" class="button" style="font-size: 100%; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; color: white; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; background: {{ brand_color }}; margin: 0; padding: 0; border-color: {{ brand_color }}; border-style: solid; border-width: 10px 20px 8px;">Complete Registration</a>
                                    </p>
                                </td>
                            </tr></table><p style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; font-weight: normal; margin: 0 0 20px; padding: 0;">Need help or have questions about how to register your product via Photoregister? Visit <a href="http://photoregister.com/help" style="font-size: 100%; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; color: {{ brand_color }}; text-decoration: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">Help Center</a>.</p>
                    </td>
                </tr></table></td>
    </tr><tr style="font-size: 100%; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; padding: 0;"><td class="container" style="font-size: 100%; font-family: 'Avenir Next', 'Helvetica Neue', 'Helvetica', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.65; display: block !important; clear: both !important; max-width: 580px !important; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0;">

            <!-- Footer start -->
